ll, don't forget to take some preventive"},{"type":"text","text":"measures.（真替他高兴。不过，别忘了采取一些保护措施。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：We have a variety of eye drops for tired eyes. Would you like"},{"type":"text","text":"one? （我们这里有很多种缓解眼睛疲劳的眼药水。来一盒吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Sure, I’d like one for children.Is this one OK? （行啊，要一盒儿"},{"type":"text","text":"童专用的。这盒可以吗？）"}]}]}